==English==
{{wikipedia|Monkey hanger}}
===Etymology===
From the alleged hanging of a "[[monkey]]", washed up into [[Hartlepool]], beleived to be a [[French]] spy during the Napoleonic wars.

===Noun===
'''Monkey Hanger'''

# {{cattag|Geordie|pejoratives}} an offensive term for a person from [[Hartlepool]].

